To do this, we'll use `fun_prop` to compute the derivative.

```tactics
  have z1 : HasFDerivAt (fun x => (rotproj_inner S w x)) (fun x => (rotproj_inner' pbar S w x)) pbar.innerParams := by
    simp [rotproj_inner, pbar]
    fun_prop
```

